OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Fremaining thundery showers, mainly
OL,7,Ffrom Aberdeen to Buchan, turning
OL,8,Flighter then dying out with a few
OL,9,Fclear intervals. Then cloud and
OL,10,Foccasional rain will spread in later
OL,11,Fin the night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,14,Frain, this turning heavy at times. A
OL,15,Ffew limited brighter intervals in
OL,16,FMoray, where it could be quite warm.
OL,17,FMore showery in evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
