OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,6,Fspells and some heavy showers Tuesday.
OL,7,FDry start Wednesday then some showers.
OL,8,FMostly cloudy with showers on
OL,9,FThursday, and quite breezy.
